---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Panduan Token API - BIG Downloader Toolbox">
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Cara Mendapatkan Token API</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg">Token diperlukan untuk mengakses data DEMNAS, BATNAS, dan RBI dari
                    server Tanah Air.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Panduan Manual -->
            <div class="rounded-2xl glass p-8 border-t border-emerald-500/20">
                <div class="space-y-6 text-slate-300">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2">Langkah 1: Buka Halaman Login</h3>
                        <p>Buka halaman <a href="https://tanahair.indonesia.go.id/portal-web/login" target="_blank"
                                class="text-emerald-400 underline">Login Ina-Geoportal</a>. <br><span
                                class="text-yellow-400 font-bold">PENTING: JANGAN Login dulu!</span> Biarkan kolom
                            username/password kosong atau terisi, tapi jangan klik tombol Masuk.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2">Langkah 2: Buka Developer Tools</h3>
                        <p>Tekan tombol <kbd class="bg-slate-700 px-2 py-1 rounded">F12</kbd> di keyboard Anda (atau
                            Klik Kanan > <i>Inspect</i>) untuk membuka panel Developer Tools. Pilih tab <b>Network</b>.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2">Langkah 3: Lakukan Login</h3>
                        <p>Setelah tab Network terbuka, silakan isi username & password Anda di halaman web, lalu klik
                            tombol <b>Masuk / Login</b>.</p>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <h3 class="font-bold text-white text-lg mb-2">Langkah 4: Filter "signin" & Salin Token</h3>
                        <p>Di daftar Network, cari nama request <code>signin</code> (gunakan kotak filter jika perlu).
                            Klik request tersebut.</p>
                        <p class="mt-2">Lihat di panel kanan (tab <b>Preview</b> atau <b>Response</b>). Cari teks
                            <code>accessToken: "..."</code>. Salin kode panjang di dalamnya.</p>
                        <div
                            class="mt-2 bg-slate-800 p-3 rounded font-mono text-xs text-emerald-300 break-all border border-slate-700">
                            Contoh Token: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1dWlkIjoiNzY3MDM4NmQt...
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-4 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-slate-700">
                        <img src="/assets/img/token_guide.png" alt="Panduan Inspect Element" class="w-full">
                        <div class="bg-slate-800 p-2 text-center text-xs text-slate-400">
                            Ilustrasi: Tab Network > Filter "signin" > Response > Ambil accessToken
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-8 bg-slate-800 p-4 rounded-lg text-sm text-yellow-500 border border-yellow-500/20">
                    ⚠ <b>Penting:</b> Token ini bersifat sementara (sekitar 1-2 jam). Jika kadaluarsa, ulangi langkah
                    ini.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
